{{Infobox Berry |name = Hondew |image = [[File:Hondew.png]] |caption = This somewhat-rare Berry projects an image of luxury, so it is favored as a gift item. |growtime = 3h 0m 0s |harvest = 23 berries |replant = 20% |points = 2,000 |flavor = {{!}} 10 {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 }} '''Hondew''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with exactly 15 points of spicy, dry and bitter and 0 points of all other flavours. The [[Figy]], [[Wiki]] and [[Aguav]] must be unlocked to unlock this berry.
